                <p><span id="said_no_01152" class="said" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Henry Tilney" data-placement="auto top">“It is amazingly; it may well
                        suggest amazement if they do — for they read nearly as many as women.
                        I myself have read hundreds and hundreds. Do not imagine that you can cope
                        with me in a knowledge of Julias and Louisas. If we proceed to particulars,
