                            kind of reading?”</span></p>

                <p><span id="said_no_01167" class="said" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Catherine Morland" data-placement="auto top">“To say the truth, I do not
                        much like any other.”</span></p>

                <p><span id="said_no_01168" class="said" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Eleanor Tilney" data-placement="auto top">“Indeed!”</span></p>

                <p><span id="said_no_01169" class="said" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Catherine Morland" data-placement="auto top">“That is, I can read poetry
                        and plays, and things of that sort, and do not dislike travels. But history,
