                <p><span id="said_no_01170" class="said" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Eleanor Tilney" data-placement="auto top">“Yes, I am fond of
                        history.”</span></p>

                <p><span id="said_no_01171" class="said" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Catherine Morland" data-placement="auto top">“I wish I were too. I read it
                        a little as a duty, but it tells me nothing that does not either vex or
                        weary me. The quarrels of popes and kings, with wars or pestilences, in
