                <p><span id="said_no_01912" class="said" data-toggle="tooltip" title="aus.003.nar" data-placement="auto top">Something had been said the
                        evening before of her being shown over the house, and he now offered himself
                        as her conductor; and though Catherine had hoped to explore it accompanied
                        only by his daughter,</span>
                    <span id="said_no_01913" class="said fid said_tooltip certainty_3" data-toggle="tooltip" title="aus.003.nar_cat" data-placement="auto top">it was a proposal of too much
                        happiness in itself, under any circumstances, not to be gladly accepted; for
                        she had been already eighteen hours in the abbey, and had seen only a few of
